<h2>Our Foolish History</h2>
<p>
The Motley Fool was founded in 1993 by brothers Tom and David Gardner as a traditional print newsletter in a backyard shed in Alexandria, Virginia. In 1994, an April Fools joke designed to teach an investing lesson put The Motley Fool on the map. Since those humble beginnings, Tom and David, and the community of Fools theyve gathered, have been leading the charge for individual investors everywhere.

</p>
